description: Royal Standard Minerals Inc. does not have significant operations. The company focuses on identifying assets or businesses to acquire or merge with a view to maximizing value for shareholders. Previously, it was engaged in the acquisition, exploration, and development of gold and precious metal properties in the United States. The company was incorporated in 1986 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Carmelo  Marrelli ACIS, B.Comm., CA, CGA, CPA
